Premier Gymnasium Equipment ... from the Industry LeaderOur philosophy of “going the extra mile” has served many gymnasium equipment customers well in a variety of markets. And it’s done so for nearly 90 years!
Architects in particular rely on us to supply them with superior gymnasium equipment for their projects. What they’ve come to expect from us are innovative solutions for gym construction, especially where design and layout functionality are concerned. 
We provide architectural designers with an unequaled range of options to accommodate different kinds of sports facilities. Little wonder, then, that many of today's top athletic arenas consider us their equipment supplier of choice.
Our staff of engineers is dedicated to new product development, innovation, and continuous improvement. We’re known for respecting safety, too. It’s foremost in our product design.

And customer service? We partner locally with exclusive distributors to maintain high levels of customer contact, availability, and personalized product support. Rest assured, all of our dealers are product certified and required to use factory-certified installers.
Go ahead. Explore our website. Take a close look at all of the gymnasium equipment and services we offer. Then contact Performance Sports Systems. We have the solutions you need!






